---
title: Honey-Soy Chicken & Jasmine Rice with Creamy Celery Slaw
description: We're channelling honey-soy flavours in this saucy chicken and jasmine rice bowl. Celery slaw adds subtle creamy softness and
honey soy sauce provides the perfect amount of sweet and salty that plays so well with golden chicken bites!
